Package: sigProCon
Type: Package
Title: Evaluate Genes Driving Signature Scores in ExpressionSet
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Author: Stefano Monti, Lina Kroehling
Maintainer: Stefano Monti <smonti@bu.edu>
Description: Given a signature and ExpressionSet, this tool computes a per-sample
    signature score using GSVA or eigengene-based scoring.
    The main purpose of this tool is to interrogate which genes are contributing most
    to the resulting signature scores.
    This tool finds the correlation of each gene in the eset with the
    produced signature score, and returns a ranked list of genes, and two heatmaps.
